
# 🧮 151. Reverse Words in a String

🔗 https://leetcode.com/problems/reverse-words-in-a-string/

## ✅ Approach:
- using a two pointer last will stay at the end of the word and first will move to the start of the word

## ⏱️ Time Complexity:
- O(n) time, O(n) space

## 🔤 Code (Java):
```java
class Solution {
    public String reverseWords(String s) {
        StringBuilder str=new StringBuilder();
        s=s.trim();
        int first=s.length()-1;
        int last=s.length()-1;

        while(first>=0){
            if(s.charAt(last)==' '){
                last--;
                first--;
            }
            else{
                if(first==0 ||s.charAt(first-1)==' '){
                str.append(s.substring(first,last+1));
                last=first-1;
                if(first!=0){
                    str.append(' ');
                }
            }
            first--;
            }
        }
        return str.toString();
    }
}
